    "text": [
        "Video games are new entertainment nowadays. They are creative and They spread in all fields. They have been made for all age groups. Most of that video games are made for children. Although  they have benefits, they have some drawbacks too. In this essay, I write about both of them.",
        "There are many  advantages of playing video games for children. The first advantage is creating coordination between the brain and hands. When children play  video games, they have to see monitors and do their activities with their hands. There are lots of levels in video games that children play section after section. Each level is different from another one. So, they learn to play with different computer gadgets at the same time. The second advantage is learning to work in a group. Most   computer video games are online games, and players have to play with other people all around the world. it does not matter how old is a player. As a result, they learn to communicate and work with other people.",
        "Although playing video games for children have benefit. It is having some disadvantages too. Playing video games for a long time cause destroys children's creativity. When they are playing games, they follow game rules and they do have not enough time to think about their environment and play mental games. It is one of the drawbacks and the second is an effect on children's behaviour. When children play video games, they imagine that they are a hero of that game, so they try to imitate the hero of the games. As a result, their behaviour  changes in the real world.",
        "In summary, playing a video game for children has lots of benefits such as creative coordination between the brain and hands and they learn working in a group. However, if they play for a long time. it has some disadvantages like, destroying creativity and changing their behaviour."
